genresAdvancedInfo.name: dutch moombahton
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Dutch moombahton is a fusion genre that combines elements of reggaeton, house music, and Dutch dance. It originated in the Netherlands and is characterized by its slow tempo, heavy basslines, and use of electronic instruments. Dutch moombahton has gained popularity in recent years, with many Dutch DJs incorporating it into their sets.
